---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About HaremLit Guide"
  description="HaremLit Guide is a reader resource for harem fantasy and men's romance fiction — published by Pivot Press Publishing, the team behind Harem-Lit.com."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#ec4899] uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">About</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">About HaremLit Guide</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8">

      <section>
        <p class="text-[#aaa] leading-relaxed">
          HaremLit Guide is a reader resource for harem fantasy and men's romance fiction — covering
          harem LitRPG, cultivation novels, reverse harem fantasy, and men's adventure romance.
          We publish ranked lists, genre guides, and new release tracking to help readers navigate a
          category that publishes hundreds of new titles every month.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="border-t border-[#2e2e2e] pt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Who Publishes This Site</h2>
        <p class="text-[#aaa] leading-relaxed">
          HaremLit Guide is published by <strong class="text-white">Pivot Press Publishing</strong> —
          the team behind <a href="https://harem-lit.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[#ec4899] hover:underline">Harem-Lit.com</a>,
          the community tracking platform for harem fantasy readers, and
          <a href="https://litrpgtools.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[#ec4899] hover:underline">LitRPGTools.com</a>.
          Pivot Press also publishes original fiction in the genre.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#aaa] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Our editorial rankings draw on community data from Harem-Lit.com. Because Pivot Press
          publishes books in the genre, some of our titles may appear in ranked lists. We include them
          because they belong there — every list is grounded in community ratings, not internal promotion.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="border-t border-[#2e2e2e] pt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our Data</h2>
        <p class="text-[#aaa] leading-relaxed">
          All book data — ratings, covers, series information, and genre classifications — is sourced from
          <a href="https://harem-lit.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[#ec4899] hover:underline">Harem-Lit.com</a>,
          which tracks harem fantasy and men's romance fiction across Amazon, Audible, and Royal Road
          using community ratings and editorial classification.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="border-t border-[#2e2e2e] pt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Amazon Affiliate Links</h2>
        <p class="text-[#aaa] leading-relaxed">
          Links to Amazon on this site are affiliate links. If you click through and make a purchase,
          we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="border-t border-[#2e2e2e] pt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-[#aaa] leading-relaxed">
          Questions or corrections? Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-[#ec4899] hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
